# Per-worktree shutdown artifacts (T-242) — generated by the SessionEnd hook
# and/or the agent on shutdown. They were accidentally committed once back in
# April 2026 and every new worktree inherited the stale files via
# `git worktree add`. The bootstrap script wipes the dir on create; this
# rule keeps anything written to it out of git going forward.
